sys/time/formatting/rfc3339.runa
RFC 3339 Timestamp Format

This module provides RFC 3339 timestamp formatting and parsing for
internet protocols. Includes support for precise timestamp formatting,
timezone offsets, and fractional seconds as specified in RFC 3339.
:End Note

